    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>開かない……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's not opening...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274132</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yeah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274192</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Dio&gt;？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Dio&gt;, are you in here?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274260</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いるんでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Please answer me.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>何イジけてるの！？
思い通りにいかないって
言われたから？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What's up with you all of a sudden!? You're acting like a 
huge thickhead! Weren't you the one that said we'd not only do 
things for our own? </EnglishText>
      <Notes>Tl check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274476</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>勝手に想像して、期待して。
それが全部裏切られたから？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>To not think only of yourself and to not carry 
everything by yourself even when things don't
go as planned...Will you betray your own beliefs?</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Tl check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274580</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>外に出る時、あんなに
はしゃいでたくせに。
バカみたい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>When you finally got to see the world, you were
so happy. Now that you know what's out there,
you shut yourself away? You look like an idiot.</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Tl check</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274672</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっと、&lt;Mel&gt;、
きみ、そんなこと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;...I think you went too far...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どうせバカだよ！
ダメダメだよ、オレ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's right! I'm a huge idiot!
I can't do anything right...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大切なエレメンツポットを
壊すし、&lt;Cless&gt;さんの代わりも
ちゃんとできない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They told me to take care of the Elements'
Pot and I broke it... Mister &lt;Cless&gt; trusted
me with his job and I failed to help him...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>274916</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;が魔物に襲われた時も
すぐ動けなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Whenever &lt;Mel&gt;'s in danger, I can't
do anything to protect her!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなこと……
気にしてたんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You've been...bottling up all
these feelings, haven't you...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_016&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>いくら色々夢見ても、
結局、全部思い通りなんて
いかないんだろ！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Even though I could finally see the
world, nothing has ever turned
out the way I wanted it to...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>バジルさんだけじゃない……
&lt;Klarth&gt;さんも、
&lt;Cless&gt;さんも&lt;Mint&gt;さんも……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've failed Mister Basil...and Mister &lt;Klarth&gt;...
and Mister &lt;Cless&gt; and Miss &lt;Mint&gt;...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんなんなら、
オレ、外なんて
出るんじゃなかった</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I don't want to see what's out
there anymore! Everything I try
to do goes wrong!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もういい。『虹輪』は
わたしひとりでなんとかする</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fine. I don't need your negativity.
I'll go stop the Prism Ring alone.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>勝手にひとりでいじけて、
とじこもって、ヤドカリに
なっちゃえばいいんだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now you can do whatever you want and
everything will turn out just how you want
it. Stay safe inside the house, you hermit!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>275968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_170_010_023&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あ、ちょっと、待って……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-Wait, &lt;Mel&gt;! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
